    <h4 class="odd">DESCRIPTION</h4> <br>

    <p>This module displays the latest news from the News module (version 1.70+) in a block.<br>.<br>

    <h4> Features:</h4>

    <ul>
        <li>Can set the number of articles to display, using one or more columns.</li>
        <li>Can choose to display the title, author, date, comments link, and other display settings.</li>
        <li>Can customize image properties in all articles (i.e. width, height, position, borders).</li>
        <li>Can customize the number of letters to truncate each news item, without cutting off any words midway.</li>
        <li>Adding link and description to each image automatically for SEO.</li>
        <li>Can limit by topic.</li>
        <li>Can display featured news only.</li>
        <li>Can clone unlimited blocks.</li>
        <li>Can scroll the articles.</li>
    </ul>
    </p><br>

